After accidentally uncovering a portal to an alternate 
universe peopled with dinosaurs, Sleestaks and other 
strange creatures, park ranger Rick Marshall (Will 
Ferrell) and his two kids are forced to navigate a 
dangerous new world. Brad Silberling directs this 
big-screen adaptation of the classic 1970s adventure 
series "Land of the Lost," the high-concept, low-budget 
fantasy dreamed up by famed children's television 
producers Sid and Marty Krofft.

Starring: Will Ferrell, Anna Friel

Director: Brad Silberling
